  description: Increases Damage of all allied heroes with the Male tag by 10%.  If
    Kaelum receives damage that reduces his HP below 20% without killing him, he
    vanishes into the void for the remainder of the turn and returns on the next
    turn, while fully restoring his Mana and increasing his Damage and Armor by 20%
    for 2 turns.
